It also has a friendship link with [[Nantong]], China.&lt;ref&gt;{{cite web |url=http://www.jiangsu.net/news/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=305:nantongs-twin-city-swansea-wales-of-uk&amp;catid=38:nantong&amp;Itemid=37 |title=Nantong's twin city: Swansea, Wales of UK |publisher=Jiangsu.net |date=12 September 2009 |accessdate=12 July 2013 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140826115803/http://www.jiangsu.net/news/index.php?option=com_content&amp;view=article&amp;id=305:nantongs-twin-city-swansea-wales-of-uk&amp;catid=38:nantong&amp;Itemid=37 |archive-date=26 August 2014 |url-status=dead }}&lt;/ref&gt;

